title: The Best Spots to Find Flan in South Florida
text:
Updated: 4:55 p.m. Monday, Sept. 28, 2015 | Posted: 5:05 a.m. Saturday, Sept. 26, 2015 The Best Spots to Find Flan in South Florida In Partnership with VisitFlorida.com 
No meal is complete without dessert, and when you're in South Florida you're going to want to get your hands on a delicious flan. Come along as Kelly Blanco introduces you to some of her favorite spots for flan, including Havana Harry's, Fireman Derek's and Rio Cristal.
